Ohhh, don’t you say it.
You just grin as you flick switches, deciding to turn up the heat a little. It’s laser time.
“Don’t be a dick, Marcus, man… I’m betting he’s great.”
“Some barely useful jet and pilot, doing gun runs, on a mainly ground battle? Sure. I thought we got some professional? Not some guy who’s going to be called Goose to lighten up his death.”
…Alright, pal. You want a show?
You break again, slowing right down.
