You pull the targeting computer out and in front of your right eye
“Thermal.”
You close your left eye and watch the visuals change, seeing the glowing outlines of multiple vehicles and suits below. All of them slightly larger and much more heavy duty then yours.
You also see the heat signatures of the bugs, smiling.
Pulling the trigger after you aim for one of the bugs, you watch the beam connect, opening your left eye to see the blue beam briefly before focusing on targeting.
Two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight, nine, te-
“Oh come on, that one was mine!” Sammy whines
